description: Reissue label Be With Records has released music by a broad range of artists, covering everyone from R&B songwriter Leon Ware to rare groove's Ned Doheny. Their mission statement is to bring unavailable music to vinyl that is otherwise currently unavailable, or perhaps was never originally released on vinyl.
